---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
import InfoCard from "@components/InfoCard.astro";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import createSlug from "../lib/createSlug";

const posts = (await getCollection("blog")).sort(
  (a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf(),
);

const last_posts = posts.slice(0, 3);
let showAlert = true;
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
  <div class="pb-12 mt-5">

{showAlert ? (
  <div class="fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4 flex items-center space-x-4 transition-transform transform">
    <span class="text-lg font-semibold"><a href="/achievers">Results have been released!</a></span>
    <button 
      onClick={() => { showAlert = false; }} 
      class="ml-4 p-2 bg-transparent border-0 text-white hover:text-gray-200 focus:outline-none">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>
) : null}



    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">Are You Ready? 🔥</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">
      The Algo-rhythmic Chase Begins!
    </div>
    <div class="text-xl py-1">Dec 27th - Jan 6th <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> "Anywhere on Earth"</div>
    <hr class="my-4" />
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
Iris returns to take you to an exciting algorithmic voyage this winter. With over <b>1000+ registrations</b> pouring in our last two editions, the excitement was palpable and the competition more fierce. Be ready to ignite your passion for programming, artificial intelligence and machine learning once again.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="py-2 text-justify">
      <text class="text-lg">
The beauty of LogicLoom lies in its accessibility. Mentoring sessions are provided to support participants in navigating the challenges, ensuring that everyone has the opportunity to excel regardless of their background. Participants also avail the opportunity to foster their spirit of teamwork and versatility in tackling various challenges as the competition unfolds. The stage is set, the challenges await - let's soar to new heights together and make it a booming success once againnnn 💥
</text>
    </div>
  
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold"><i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i> Announcements</div>

    <div class="divider my-0"></div>

